    <h4>The Sonia Shankman Orthogenic School</h4>
    <p>The Orthogenic School is a residential and day school for bright students who are coping with profound emotional challenges. Over the course of nearly 100 years, the O-School’s distinctive blend of academic rigor and relationship-based treatment has enabled more than 80 percent of students to return home to their families and mainstream schools.</p>
    <p><a class="btn btn-mini" href="#">Info on the O-School &raquo;</a></p>
