    <h4>The Hyde Park Day School</h4>
    <p>Hyde Park Day School offers bright students with learning disabilities an innovative and comprehensive education. Our intensive, individualized curriculum prepares students for successful transitions to mainstream schools.  Our teachers and staff focus on academic and self-advocacy skills in a collaborative environment, enhancing students’ self-esteem and self confidence while fostering a positive attitude toward learning.</p>
    <p><a class="btn btn-mini" href="#">Info on the HPDS &raquo;</a></p>
